kground-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">（5）“干干净净的蓝天上，偷偷溜来一团乌云，风推着它爬上山头。山这边，梯田里的庄稼，像绿海里卷来的一道道浪头”一句运用的修辞手法是比喻。 </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 25px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">（6）“它们是从谁家来的，又飞到谁家去？”这句话朗读时应该用高升调。 </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 25px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">（7）“明晃晃”、“毛嘟嘟”、“笑眯眯”、“蓝幽幽”这四个叠词的结构是一样的。 </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 25px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">（8）“一霎时”和“一刹那”意思相同，其中“霎”和“刹”的读音也相同。  </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 25px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 25px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">【答案】</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-